             sworn. - I am a <rs id="t18011028-72-viclabel387" type="occupation">broker and auctioneer</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18011028-72-victim634 t18011028-72-viclabel387"></join>; I advertized a sale on the 25th of September, at Holborn-hill, and I was informed a counterpane was stolen, which I am answerable for.</p>

               <p>- sworn. - I went to the attic story to get the sale ready, and saw the prisoner in a disagreeable situation; I thought he had taken something, and followed him down, and took him at the bottom of the house, with the counterpane in his breeches.</p>
               <p>Mrs. LLOYD sworn. - I know it to be the counterpane that covered the children's bed.(
               <persName id="t18011028-72-person636">
                  James 
                  Coleman
               <interp inst="t18011028-72-person636" type="surname" value="Coleman"></interp>
