                     <interp inst="t18011028-72-person636" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             produced a bunch of keys, and the counterpane, which were identified by Mrs. Lloyd.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I'll thank your Lordship to shew me mercy.</p>
               <p>GUILTY, aged 66.</p>
